    "body": "## Problem\r\n\r\nEntries in `errorformat` can contain escaped commas, and `vim.split(errorformat, ',')` in this case gets incorrect table.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n\r\nProcess `errorformat` one char after another to not treat escaped commas as a separator.\r\n\r\nFixes #29061",
